OL,4,Cfacing investigation over alleged
OL,5,Cbetting
OL,7,FRussell George, a Conservative member
OL,8,Fof the Senedd, has stepped back from
OL,9,Fthe Welsh shadow cabinet as he faces
OL,10,Fan investigation by the gambling
OL,11,Fwatchdog over alleged bets on the
OL,12,Ftiming of the General Election.
OL,14,FIt comes as the Conservative Party had
OL,15,Fwithdrawn its support for a Welsh
OL,16,Fcandidate Craig Williams, who was
OL,17,Fcaught up in allegations of betting on
OL,18,Fthe date of the timing of the UK
OL,19,FGeneral Election.
