OL,4,Cfacing investigation over alleged
OL,5,Cbetting
OL,7,FMr George said: "Whilst I will
OL,8,Fcooperate fully with the Gambling
OL,9,FCommission, it would not be
OL,10,Fappropriate to comment on this
OL,11,Findependent and confidential process.
OL,13,F"Doing so would only jeopardise and
OL,14,Fundermine the investigation. It is the
OL,15,FGambling Commission, not the media,
OL,16,Fthat has the responsibility, powers
OL,17,Fand resources to properly investigate
OL,18,Fthese matters and determine what, if
OL,19,Fany, action should be taken.
